Class ReversiModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.ReversiModel
  • public class ReversiModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Ryan This is the model for my reversi board. It is only ever called by the controller, or by testers. The board is represented as an 8x8 char[][] array.
